text:
Hey Guys, I am trying to loop through the widgets on a page and set a variable to true if one of the widgets meets a certain criteria. Essentially it works but only inside the loop. If I try and output the variable outside of the loop, its value is still false. Does anyone know if there is a workaround for this? Here is my example:

```{% set my_var = false %} // set default value

{% for widget in content.widgets %}

   {% if widget.body.something == true %}
      {% set my_var = true %}
   {% endif %}

   {{ my_var }} // outputs correctly as true
{% endfor %}

{{ my_var }} // outputs as false```
Many thanks!
